da_margins":0.09342,"gross_margins":0.33771,"operating_margins":0.046230003,"profit_margins":0.01253,"net_income":38708000.0,"total_cash":14548000.0,"total_cash_per_share":0.104,"total_debt":781494016.0,"debt_to_equity":36.865,"enterprise_value":3009160960.0,"enterprise_to_ebitda":10.425,"enterprise_to_revenue":0.974,"earnings_growth":2.86,"shares_outstanding":139530000.0,"float_shares":30586371.0,"held_pct_insiders":0.76139,"held_pct_institutions":0.0,"beta":-0.65,"fifty_two_week_high":46.96,"fifty_two_week_low":14.85,"fifty_day_average":20.0626,"two_hundred_day_avg":31.929874,"recommendation":"none","all_time_high":75.95,"all_time_low":8.2525,"long_business_summary":"Pavna Industries Limited, together with its subsidiaries, manufactures and sells automotive components in India and internationally. The company's automotive components include ignition switches, fuel tank caps, latches, auto locks, handles, bar switches, oil and water pumps, carburetors, chain tensioners, throttle bodies, fuel cocks and pumps, injection systems, engine and casting components, etc.; and aftermarket products comprising filters, clutch plates, bearings, wiper blades, and brake shoes. It also offers steering cum ignition lock assembly, handle bar switch, lever assembly, side stand sensor, regulator rectifier unit, LCM light control, magnet holder, termination unit, and wire harness products; headlights, mirrors, control cable, blinkers, and air filters; and accessories, such as wheel, helmet, disc brake, and cable locks, as well as horns and foot rests. In addition, the company provides aftermarket sales and services. It offers its components for passenger vehicles, two-wheelers, three-wheelers, heavy and light commercial vehicles, off-road vehicles, and electric vehicles. Pavna Industries Limited was formerly known as Pavna Zadi Security Systems Limited and changed its name to Pavna Industries Limited in May 2019. Pavna Industries Limited was incorporated in 1971 and is based in Aligarh, India."}}